ground truth PDB's
query.fasta -> fasta from which the PDB's were predicted (TODO: were did this come from)
pdb.fasta -> as ground truth PDBs might miss some amino acids that were found in the query.fasta, we generate a fasta of sequences consisting of amino acids that were actually in the PDB
proteins.txt -> list of all the PDB's considered
alignment.fasta -> MSA between all sequences in pdb.fasta and query.fasta

pdb.fasta and alignment.fasta were generated by scripts/fasta.sh
